list.abstract: usually（英[ˈjuːʒuəli]，美[ˈjuːʒuəli]），英语单词。做副词用，指通常、经常、一般等。例句为Mid-Autumn Day usually comes on August 15th in the lunar calendar every year.（中秋节通常在每年的农历八月十五）。 近义词有generally、mostly；反义词为remarkably。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yes, but there's usually planning, courtship, advance notice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有的，但通常要计划，求爱，并且提前通知。

yingyinNormal.en: So, it's not surprising that crave-ability usually means adding calories.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此这并不让人感到意外，渴望通常意味着额外的热量摄取。

yingyinNormal.en: When I go, I usually just get hammered and ride the cable cars.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我通常只去玩击锤和坐缆车。

yingyinNormal.en: No, actually, one is because I am usually better than this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，实际上一个是因为我通常做得更好。

yingyinNormal.en: It turns out that we usually think that we observe reality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 调查显示我们通常认为现实是观察到的。

yingyinNormal.en: Now usually my numbered stick would be read by a fortune teller.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通常是要把签条拿给算命先生看的。

yingyinNormal.en: Raj, what about you? Oh, he usually comes to my house. Right, pal?
yingyinNormal.zh: 拉杰，你呢？他通常都去我家过节，对吧？

yingyinNormal.en: And girls like that are challenging. It's true. They're complicated and enigmatic and usually worth it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的，这种女孩通常都喜欢给你出难题，她们内心复杂... 难以琢磨，但通常也值得。

yingyinNormal.en: He isn't home from the gym yet. Usually you call us in the morning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他还没从健身房回来，你通常都是早上打电话。

yingyinNormal.en: I have to admit usually when guys ask me out they're not after my blood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要承认通常男人约我可不会是想抽我的血。

yingyinNormal.en: That was fast. It usually takes me hours to get Ben to go down for his nap.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真快，我通常要花2小时才能让班乖乖睡觉。

yingyinNormal.en: What do you do? I usually go play Tetris on somebody else's computer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你怎么办呢？我通常会到别人的电脑上玩俄罗斯方块。

yingyinNormal.en: Whoever brought in the most money after six months was usually hired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通常情况下6个月内为公司揽到最多生意的人将被雇用。

yingyinNormal.en: Gee, Sheldon, you're asking the wrong girl. I'm usually on the other side of the tie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，你问错人了，我通常在领带的另一边。

yingyinNormal.en: Amy. I usually know exactly what to say. But in this moment, I have no words.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾米，我通常都明确知道自己要说什么。但此刻，我无以言表。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm usually really good with names and faces, but I could not remember who this guy was.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我通常很擅长记名字和脸，可我不记得这个人是谁了。

yingyinNormal.en: Usually when everything is normal, people don't respond in perfectly rehearsed unison.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通常当一切正常时，人们不会回答得这么一致，像排练过一样。

yingyinNormal.en: When those two markets mixed, something happens. And that thing is usually not very good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这两者混在一起时，就会有事情发生，通常都是不好的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: I know. It's just you know usually when you're done with the pregnant thing, you know, then you get to do the mom thing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道，只是通常怀孕完之后就是当妈妈。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, the simplest explanation is usually the right one. Which is? That ain't Sheldon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最简单的解释通常也是最正确的解释。什么解释？那不是谢尔顿。
